title: pimutils: coreutils for personal information management
---
body:

pimutils is a suite of programs for managing contacts, calendars and tasks on the command line.

* [khal](https://github.com/pimutils/khal) is a CLI calendar application
* [todoman](https://github.com/pimutils/khal) is a CLI tasks application
* [vdirsyncer](https://github.com/pimutils/vdirsyncer) can synchronize the data from khal and todoman with external servers
